	value of XML_GetCurrentLineNumber and XML_GetCurrentColumnNumber to
	size_t and use %zu
	* nih-dbus-tool/node.c (node_start_tag): Likewise.
	* nih-dbus-tool/interface.c (interface_start_tag): Likewise.
