2006-08-18  Scott James Remnant  <scott@netsplit.com>

	* TODO: Update.

	* nih/main.h (nih_main_init_gettext): Macro that expands to the
	usual gettext initialisation spiel if ENABLE_NLS is set, or nothing
	if not.
